<title>LUTHER'S HYMN</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Gamtin ah Kross thihna lul hi,
 Hung thang suok hen, khawk tak ahi;
 Kalvari ah khuo hungvak hen,
 Gamtin muoltin hun salhvak hen (2)

[V2]
 2. Lalpa ka Pathien na nasep,
 Kawl kimvel tiengin suhalh in;
 Na lungsiet zawh theih ngeiloh hi,
 Gamtin ah hun hih lang inla (2)</lyrics>
</song>